---------------
1.  WHAT's NEW
---------------
A list of changes in recent versions:

0.8.6: (21-Sep-2005):
  * [BUG] The ImageIO module was not initialized properly.

  * The JDK 1.4 printing has been redesigned. Now the report page definition
    properties get fully mapped into IPP-properties.

0.8.5-5: (04-Mar-2005)
  * New Chart-Demo shows how to print multiple charts in a single report.

0.8.5: (04-Mar-2005)
  * Experimental barcode classes.

  * The servlet demo has been update to demonstrate the use of URLImageReferences.

  * The chart demo now uses the latest JFreeChart jar.

0.8.4-5: (1-Nov-2003):
	* The JDK1.4-Printing is more configurable now. The appearance in the menus of the
	  preview components can be redefined.

  * A new demo shows the use of the DrawableElement to display JFreeCharts.
	  Better support for charts will be implemented after version 0.8.5

0.8.4-4: (1-Nov-2003):
	* Removed obsolete test classes

0.8.4: (19-Oct-2003) :
  * BugFix: Java1.4 printing did not show the progress monitor.
  
  * Warning: Java1.4 printing does not accept changes of the 
    pageformat or the borders and will not show the number of pages
    of the report yet. 

0.8.2: (12-Apr-2003) :
  * Nothing new, just a release to keep in sync with the main project.

0.8.1_01: (04-Mar-2003) :

  * This is the initial official version of the extension project
  
  * Added a WebApplication to show how to use JFreeReport in a Servlet 
    environment
    
  * Added a Java1.4 log target
  

23-Jun-2002: 
  * JUnit Test added to the extension project
	
  * Log4J-LogTarget added

